<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="topnav">
      <a class="active" href="../">Home</a>
      <a href="offers/index">Search Pokemon Offers</a>
      <a href="requests/index">Request Trade</a>
      <% if (user) { %>
        <a href="/logout">LOG OUT</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/auth/google" class="login">LOG IN&nbsp;<img src="https://i.imgur.com/FHjYyi0.png"></a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <p>Here you can search a pokemon you are looking for!</p>
    <p>Someone out there may be trying to trade a pokemon you want.</p>
    <p>Or maybe you want to add a pokemon that you are willing to trade.</p>
    <p>You can coordinate the trades with someone and get your desired pokemon!</p>
    <img src='<%= pokeName.sprites.other['official-artwork'].front_default %>'>
